descriptionHtml:
Tap the screen to jump and score as many points as possible! The game "Flappy Dunk : Stack Jump Game" is a new, entertaining and fun jumping and flying game for all categories where the player must press the screen constantly to jump the yellow bird and enter the middle of the white discs, but must avoid falling to the bottom. Fly with the yellow bird and avoid falling over the cactus by jumping and flying and entering the middle of the white discs and collecting the largest number of points. "Flappy Dunk : Stack Jump Game" is a free and great game for all players and it is a game of jumping and flying in the sky. To fly with the yellow bird you must hold down the screen and jump over the white discs. how to play: -Tap the screen to jump the resulting bird. Try to fly the yellow bird over the cactus poles. Avoid falling on the cactus poles by jumping and flying. - Try to collect the largest number of points by flying and jumping for the longest time in the sky. Don't miss the chance to fly and jump with the yellow bird through the fun and free "Flappy Dunk : Stack Jump Game" for everyone. With this game, you will enjoy flying and jumping in the sky and over the cactus pillars with the yellow bird that will become your best and close friend. Features of "Flappy Dunk : Stack Jump Game": - Fun and beautiful graphics. Flying in the sky and jumping over the cactus pillars. Unlimited flight with the yellow bird. To contact us,

Jump Modes:
Keep Jump: Press, jump, fall in the blocks. Control the jumper jumping in the boxes. Single mode and battle mode free to choose. Do block jump as far as you can, and never stop! Are you ready?

Stack Jump: How high can you climb? Jump to stack blocks and build the biggest tower imaginable! Be careful, the blocks are moving with different speed. Stack up the blocks and jump up as high as you can! Play the stacking game and compete for the best score.

Dunk Shoot: Ready to shoot some circles? Control flying ball and start dunking! Dunk Shoot is a burning hot arcade game that anybody can enjoy! Shoot the flappy ball in the hoops, the same as basketball hoops. Tap to jump into as many hoops as possible.

Flying Bird: Tap to control flappy wings and fly between walls to get the highest possible score. Fun and addictive jumping game, best time killer free for all ages. Test your patience and attention.

Tower Jump: The longer the press is the further the man can jump. You just be careful do not let the jumpman fall off the tower, or the game is over. Try it out and have fun! Let’s see who can jump higher!

Kungfu Jump: In this mode, you will enter into a Kungfu jumping world. Mysterious interface design and Chinese ninja create a unique jump world. Release you in the world and jump smash.

Bounce Balls: Balls vs blocks! Swipe your finger and roll the ball, break all bricks and finish all puzzle challenges. Unique combination between ball brick breaker games and jump ball shoot games, perfect time killer to spend your leisure time. Relax your brain in the addicted ball bounce shooting games!
